\pard\plain \tx1123\tx1685\tx2246\tx2794\tx3355\tx3917\tx4478\tx5040\tx5602\tx6163\tx6725\fi720\ri-720\sl288\slmult1\ql\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 That night revealed a cloud of stars. These were prime walking hours, for the world was blue and chilly. They passed by distant dunes with dark streaks in them. Moto called them weeping dunes. Large weeping dunes. The dark lines were streaks of water seeping out onto the surface. }
